Come to think of it, I seem to 
recall doing this last year...

248
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,310
I should've had you guys 
help me from the start.

249
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:59,270
That would defeat the 
purpose of the homework.

250
00:14:59,270 --> 00:15:02,270
I'll be finished by tonight at this rate.

251
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:05,750
Yeah, I guess there'll 
be no more Armageddon.

252
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:08,710
Hey, let's do <i>that.</i>

253
00:15:08,710 --> 00:15:09,490
Huh?

254
00:15:09,490 --> 00:15:13,880
Something even scarier 
than Armageddon...

255
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:18,850
Let's do a test of courage!

256
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,800
Since you called at night,

257
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:23,900
I thought you wanted to light 
fireworks, so I brought some.

258
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:27,980
We're not doing fireworks. 
We're doing a test of courage.

259
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:32,310
I actually wanted to do it at a graveyard...

